dc_title_s: Hunter's addition to Ypsilanti; Surveyed and plated by Samuel Pettibone.
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. Shows Hunter's Addition subdivison to the City of Ypsilanti, Michigan. 1 map: manuscript; 81 x 62 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
